Rulings.Goat:
●The effect of “Paladin of White Dragon” states that “Blue-Eyes White Dragon” cannot attack that turn. Does this mean any “Blue-Eyes White Dragon” on the field or the one that was Special Summoned by “Paladin of White Dragon”? 
A: It refers to the “Blue Eyes White Dragon” that was Special Summoned from the effect of “Paladin of White Dragon.”
